























the unreliable tool pushes intentions to a deeper level by leading to
the exploration of alternative paths

an intelligent mind readily reacts when assumptions prove false, here
is the multidirectionality of will

even when other people are not involved

like being alone

being offline or being offgrid is tough, but it points me to what lasts

trasforma il controllo in comunicazione

resilienza, antifragilità

apprendimento, comunicazione

multidirezionalità del controllo